The paper discusses the behavior of systems in response to changing environments, which is a key topic in the field of systems engineering (cs.SY). The paper also proposes a metric space for behaviors, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the optimization of system-environment fit, which is a topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and systems integration (cs.SI).
